name: Lady Mascott chapter 2 - Delirium Phase: Destination of My Thoughts.
description:
Lady Mascott - Chapter 2.
Second piece.
-----
 
Passed midnight.
Cold sweat, cold face.

Mind chasing ghost.
When my body souless bellow.

Fire flies on the walls ,
between dimensions knocking.
Rotation on horizon.

Bruises cover my skin.
 Vains ropes on the neck.

My body phasing daily,
Like three of them floating.

Cannot understand what it is.
Maybe, it’s just pills and chemical singing.
